description: Attention Investors / Developers: Great 3 unit building located on West 8th St in South Boston.  It is conveniently located, close to public transportation and walking distance to red line . Great value, don't miss this unique opportunity.. Please do your own due diligence regarding dimensions, occupancy, permits, etc. Unit 2 and 3 are empty. This property features a spacious backyard and includes a deeded right-of-way (common passage). The neighboring property has utilized this passage as a driveway and added three off-street parking spaces. Similar improvements should be possible for this property, offering excellent potential for adding off street parking. Property requires TLC and is being sold in 'as-is' condition.  Great possibility to add a roof deck with great views of city skyline.  Agent or owner is not making any representations on what can be done with property or with passage in common.
